name: Snaptaztic
description: Hampton Roads Premier Photo Booth Rental
overview:
Looking for a unique way to have fun at your special event? You found it… Snaptaztic photo booths! Combine the fun photo booth experience you remember as a kid with today’s digital photo technologies and the result is a fun, fast and affordable experience that your guests will love.

Our booths are unlike any others you will find out there. Our booth appearance, functionality, high-quality photographic equipment and friendly staff ensure the very best guest experience. We’re also realistic enough to know that quality carries a price… but we promise that we’ll customize a package to work with every budget so that you don’t have to cut corners and accept compromises elsewhere.
